你能够调用以下的API:
[['CryptoNews.get_recent_news', {'name': 'CryptoNews.get_recent_news', 'description': 'This function retrieves recent news articles about a specific cryptocurrency.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'crypto', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The cryptocurrency to search news for, e.g., bitcoin, ethereum.'}, {'name': 'duration', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The duration for which to retrieve news, e.g., 1 week, 1 month.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'news', 'description': 'A list of up to five news articles about the cryptocurrency.'}]}], ['CryptoMarket.get_price_history', {'name': 'CryptoMarket.get_price_history', 'description': 'This function retrieves historical price data for a cryptocurrency.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'crypto', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The cryptocurrency to retrieve price history for.'}, {'name': 'duration', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The duration for which to retrieve price history, e.g., 30 days, 1 year.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'price_history', 'description': 'Historical price data for the cryptocurrency.'}]}], ['CryptoMarket.get_current_price', {'name': 'CryptoMarket.get_current_price', 'description': 'This function retrieves the current price of a cryptocurrency.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'crypto', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The cryptocurrency to retrieve the current price for.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'current_price', 'description': 'The current price of the cryptocurrency.'}]}], ['CryptoMarket.get_crypto_details', {'name': 'CryptoMarket.get_crypto_details', 'description': 'This function retrieves detailed information about a cryptocurrency.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'crypto', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The cryptocurrency to retrieve details for.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'details', 'description': 'Detailed information about the cryptocurrency, including market cap, volume, and supply.'}]}], ['InvestmentStrategy.suggest_strategy', {'name': 'InvestmentStrategy.suggest_strategy', 'description': 'This function suggests an investment strategy for a cryptocurrency.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'crypto', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The cryptocurrency to suggest a strategy for.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'strategy', 'description': 'An investment strategy for the cryptocurrency, considering market trends and volatility.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `CryptoNews.get_recent_news` 并传入 `crypto` 和 `duration`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "CryptoNews.get_recent_news",
    "args": "{'crypto': 'bitcoin', 'duration': '1 week'}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
